description: This Fourth Edition to NIST-JANAF (Joint Army-Navy-Air Force) Thermochemical Tables contains tables of recommended temperature-dependent values for the standard enthalpy of formation Gibbs (free) energy of formation, the logarithm of equilibrium constant of formation, the heat capacity, entropy, enthalpy, and Gibbs energy function for 48 elements and many of their compounds.  This publication is a current collection of all tables issued through 1997 under contracts with the U.S. Departement of Energy and the U.S. Air Force Office of Scientific Research, NASA, the JANNAF Combustion Subcommittee, and the SRD Program.
